long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A chrome extension for connecting to LinkedIn people faster. Built using React. 

The extension gets activated whenever you visit a LinkedIn people search page. It shows the people in that page and upon clicking connect, it sends connection request to them.
